message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item holds significant value to me, but I understand its worth from your perspective. I am offering it to you for $10,000, which I believe strikes a fair balance between its intrinsic value and what you perceive its worth to be. This is an exclusive opportunity tailored to your needs, and I'm confident it will meet your expectations. Please let me know if this offer aligns with your considerations.
